==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: interlingua
<hw>in`ter*lin"gua</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A language used
as an intermediate language in translating from a source language to a
target language; -- used especially in machine translation by computers;
<as>as, some machine translation systems use Esperanto as an
<ex>interlingua</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interlining</ent>⟦br⟧
